===========
 AUTOREPLY 
===========
| 

about
-----
| 

:author:  Bart Thate <bthate@gmail.com>
:contact: IRCNET/#dunkbots
:distribution: core
:license: Public Domain
 
| 

description
-----------
| 

jabber autoreply

| 

  do autoreply on incoming jabber private messages except commands. to enable
  use autoreply-cfg txt <message to send>. 

| 

commands
--------
| 

1) *autoreply-cfg*

    :description: plugin configuration

    :permissions: OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !autoreply-cfg
        <output> options: txt="" .. version="GOZERBOT 0.9"


2) *autoreply-cfgsave*

    :description: save plugin configuration

    :permissions: OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !autoreply-cfgsave
        <output> config saved


3) *autoreply-disable*

    :description: disable the autoreply functionality

    :permissions: OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !autoreply-disable
        <output> autoreply is disabled


